### HYMN XXV

#### A charm to remove pustules or scrofulous swellings (apachitas)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0602501">1</span></span>May all the
five-and-fifty which meet round the tendons of the  
   neck.  
  Depart and vanish hence away like plaguing insects buzz and  
   hum!  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0602502">2</span></span>Those
seventy-and-seven which meet round the upper vertebrae,  
  Let them all vanish hence away like plaguing insects' buzz and  
   hum!  
<span class="margnote"><span id="an_0602503">3</span></span>Those
nine-and-ninety which, combined, attack the shoulder  
   round about,  
  Let them all vanish hence away like plaguing insects' buzz and  
   hum!

